"
" Vim Plugins
"
" Adding plugins here is enough. Retrieving them is automated.
"
" vim-polyglot is a collection of language packs
Plug 'sheerun/vim-polyglot'

" vim-rails for editing Ruby on Rails applications
Plug 'tpope/vim-rails'

" git-gutter shows a git diff in the 'gutter'
" It shows if a line is modified, added or removed
Plug 'airblade/vim-gitgutter'

" Colorscheme gruvbox-material
Plug 'sainnhe/gruvbox-material'
